/******************************************************************************                      
** Name		 : USP_PV_GetManagerAccount                      
** Short Desc: Get All Manager and Specific Accounts associated to the Client. 
**                      
** Full Description: Get All Manager and Specific Accounts associated to the Client.
**      
**                              
** Input Arguments:  
	@AccountType		: @AccountType value tobe searched.          
    
**         
** Sample Call          
 EXEC USP_PV_GetManagerAccount 'GAP'  
**             
**                      
**                      
** Standard declarations                      
**       SET LOCK_TIMEOUT         30000   -- 30 seconds                      
